<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Setup Two-Factor Authentication</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f5ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 70, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #001f5c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .qr-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .instructions {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .secret-key {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: monospace;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #001f5c;
        }
        
        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccd7ea;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        .button {
            background-color: #003399;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #00286b;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            color: #d32f2f;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Setup Two-Factor Authentication</h1>
        
        <div class="instructions">
            <p>Follow these steps to set up two-factor authentication:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Download an authenticator app like Google Authenticator, Authy, or Microsoft Authenticator on your mobile device.</li>
                <li>Scan the QR code below with your authenticator app.</li>
                <li>Enter the 6-digit verification code from your authenticator app to verify setup.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="qr-container">
            <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code for 2FA">
        </div>
        
        <p>If you can't scan the QR code, you can manually enter this secret key into your authenticator app:</p>
        <div class="secret-key">
            <%= secret %>
        </div>
        
        <% if (locals.error) { %>
            <div class="error-message">
                <%= error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <form action="/verify-2fa-setup" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="token">Verification Code</label>
                <input type="text" id="token" name="token" placeholder="Enter 6-digit code" required>
            </div>
            
            <button type="submit" class="button">Verify and Activate</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 